{"title_page": "List of Goldie & Bear episodes", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{italic title|string=Goldie & Bear}}\nThis is a list of the ''[[Goldie & Bear]]'' episodes aired by [[Disney Junior]]. The first season has been released, while the second season has also released as well. Episodes for Season 1 were announced in 2013.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.disneyabcpress.com/disneyjunior/shows/goldie-bear/ |title=Goldie & Bear Newest episodes |access-date=23 February 2013}}</ref>\n\nOn June 29, 2018, Disney Junior cancelled the series. The series finale aired on October 1, 2018.\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{| class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+\n! colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\" |Season\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Segments\n! rowspan=\"2\" |Episodes\n! colspan=\"2\" |Originally aired\n|-\n!First aired\n!Last aired\n|-\n| style=\"background:#800080;\" |\n|[[List of Goldie and Bear episodes #Season 1 (2015\u201316)|1]]\n|43\n|22\n|{{Start date|2015|9|12}}\n|{{End date|2016|8|15}}\n|-\n| style=\"background:#0000EE;\" |\n||[[List of Goldie and Bear episodes #Season 2 (2017\u201318)|2]]\n|45\n|23\n|{{Start date|2017|9|18}}<ref name=\"GoldieandZap2it\">{{cite web|url=https://tvlistings.zap2it.com/overview.html?programSeriesId=SH02258494&tmsId=SH022584940000&from=sl&aid=gapzap|title=Goldie & Bear|publisher=Zap2it|access-date=January 7, 2018}}</ref>\n|{{End date|2018|10|1}}\n|-\n|\n|[[3]]\n|TBA\n|TBA\n|May 1, 2020\n|TBA\n|}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Episodes==\n===Season 1 (2015\u201316)===\n{{Episode table\n|background      = #800080\n|overall         = 3\n|season          = 3\n|title           = 30\n|director        = 25\n|writer          = 20\n|airdate         = 17\n|episodes        =\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 1\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 1\n| Title = The Birthday Chair\"<hr>\"Big Bear\n| DirectedBy = Chris Gilligan\n| WrittenBy = Mike Rabb<hr>[[Jorge Aguirre (author)|Jorge Aguir