bb\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|1|25}}\n\n| ShortSummary = *'''All the King Men:''' The king's men forbid everything.\n*'''Cheshire Goldie:''' When Goldie accidentally becomes invisible, she uses her newfound power to trick her friends.\n| LineColor=800080\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 12\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 12\n| Title = The Troll Tamer\"<hr>\"The Froggiest Prince of All\n| DirectedBy = Chris Gilligan\n| WrittenBy = Claudia Silver<hr>Bart Jennett\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|2|1}}\n\n| ShortSummary = *'''The Troll Tamer:''' Goldie trains Bear to be a troll tamer and accidentally wakes up a real Troll.\n*'''The Froggiest Prince of All:''' Bear and Humpty transform Frog into Goldie\u2019s favorite hero, Prince Charming.\n| LineColor=800080\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 13\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 13\n| Title = Bear Who Would Be King\"<hr>\"When the Gnome is Away\n| DirectedBy = Chris Gilligan\n| WrittenBy = Mike Rabb\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|2|8}}\n\n| ShortSummary = *'''Bear Who Would Be King:''' Bear is declared King of Fairy Tale Forest when he removes a sword from a stone.\n*'''When the Gnome is Away:''' While house sitting for Gnome, Goldie and Bear open a magic jar that brings everything to life.\n| LineColor=800080\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 14\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 14\n| Title = Training of the Broom\"<hr>\"Hickory Dickory Brian\n| DirectedBy = Chris Gilligan\n| WrittenBy = Claudia Silver and Jorge Aguirre<hr>Bart Jennett\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|3|21}}\n\n| ShortSummary = *'''Training of the Broom:''' When Goldie and Bear find a lost witch\u2019s broom, they take turns watching after it.\n*'''Hickory Dickory Brian:''' Goldie and Bear help their friend Brian the Mouse who is convinced he is jinxed.\n| LineColor=800080\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber = 15\n| EpisodeNumber2 = 15\n| Title = Giant Among Us\"<hr>\"Fetch Skippy Fetch\n| DirectedBy = Chris Gilligan\n| WrittenBy = Mike Rabb<h