 bag of doubling dust and instead of 1 there are 3 Sprinkles causing mischief around Fairytale Forest.\n*'''Trick or Treat Trouble:''' Goldie and Bear try their new Halloween costumes. Originally, Bear goes as a sandwich and Goldie as a wizard of stuff around the house. But when Goldie doesn't like her costume and dresses up as a sandwich too, Bear gets jealous and sad because her costume is better and she copied his idea. In the end, they both turn up to Ginger's Halloween party with Goldie as a sandwich and Bear as a milkshake. [[Series Finale]]\n| LineColor=0000EE\n}}\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Goldie And Bear Episodes, List Of}}\n[[Category:Lists of American children's animated television series episodes]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{italic title|string=Goldie & Bear}}\nThis is a list of the ''[[Goldie & Bear]]'' episodes aired by [[Disney Junior]]. The first season has been released, while the second season has also released as well. Episodes for Season 1 were announced in 2013.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.disneyabcpress.com/disneyjunior/shows/goldie-bear/ |title=Goldie & Bear Newest episodes |access-date=23 February 2013}}</ref>\n\nOn June 29, 2018, Disney Junior cancelled the series. The series finale aired on October 1, 2018.\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Segments\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Episodes\n!colspan=\"2\"|Originally aired\n|-\n!First aired\n!Last aired\n|-\n|style=\"background:#800080;\"|\n|[[List of Goldie and Bear episodes #Season 1 (2015\u201316)|1]]\n|43\n|22\n|{{Start date|2015|9|12}}\n|{{End date|2016|8|15}}\n|-\n|style=\"background:#0000EE;\"|\n||[[List of Goldie and Bear episodes #Season 2 (2017\u201318)|2]]\n|45\n|23\n|{{Start date|2017|9|18}}<ref name=\"GoldieandZap2it\">{{cite web|url=https://tvlistings.zap2it.com/overview.html?programSeriesId=SH02258494&tmsId