{"title_page": "Derrick Pierce", "text_new": "{{Infobox adult biography\n| name         = Derrick Pierce\n| image        = Derrick Pierce 2014.jpg\n| caption      = Derrick Pierce in [[Hollywood]], [[California]] on December 5, 2014\n| birth_name   = \n| birth_date   = {{birth date and age|mf=yes|1974|3|1}}<ref name=IAFD>{{iafd name|id=derrickpierce|gender=male|name=Derrick Pierce}}</ref>\n| birth_place  = {{nowrap|[[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]], [[Massachusetts]], U.S.}}\n| death_date   = \n| death_place  = \n| spouse       = \n| height       = {{height|ft=6|in=0}}<ref name=DieScreaming>{{cite web|url= http://www.die-screaming.com/derrick-pierce-interview-4123/|title= 7 Questions with Derrick Pierce|accessdate= March 15, 2015|author= Dan C.|date= October 31, 2013|publisher= Die-Screaming}}</ref>\n| weight       = {{convert|210|lb|kg st|abbr=on}}<ref name=DieScreaming/>\n| alias        = \n| number_of_films = 954 as performer, 5 as director (per [[IAFD]])<ref name=IAFD/>\n| website      = \n}}\n\n'''Derrick Pierce''' (born March 1, 1974) is an American [[pornographic actor]], director, radio personality, and personal trainer.<ref name=IAFD/><ref name=YNOT/><ref name=Radio/> Pierce has received several adult industry awards, including the 2009 [[NightMoves Award]] for Best Male Performer and the 2016 [[XRCO Award]] for Best Actor.<ref name=NM/>\n\n==Early life==\nPierce was born in [[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]], [[Massachusetts]] and raised in [[Los Angeles]], [[California]]. He is of [[French people|French]] and [[Italians|Italian]] descent.<ref name=IAFD/> He was raised by a single mother whom he credits as being an extremely strong influence in his life and the primary reason for his intense appreciation of women. His mother was also in the entertainment world,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.adultmaven.com/articles/4607/1/Derrick-Pierce-Interview/Page1.html |title=Archived copy |access-date=2008-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/w