 || 2\u20131\n|-\n| 35. || 2 July 2007 || {{fb|Colombia}} || 1\u20131 \u2021 || 4\u20132\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n'''River Plate'''<ref name=SW>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/coaches/hernan-jorge-crespo/117/|title=H. Crespo|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=27 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]]: [[1993\u201394 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|1993 (Apertura)]], [[1994\u201395 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|1994 (Apertura)]]\n*[[Copa Libertadores]]: [[1996 Copa Libertadores Finals|1996]]\n\n'''Parma'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Coppa Italia]]: [[1998\u201399 Coppa Italia|1998\u201399]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[1999 Supercoppa Italiana|1999]]\n*[[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Cup|1998\u201399]]\n\n'''Lazio'''<ref name=SW/>\n*Supercoppa Italiana: [[2000 Supercoppa Italiana|2000]]\n\n'''A.C. Milan'''<ref name=SW/>\n*Supercoppa Italiana: [[2004 Supercoppa Italiana|2004]]\n\n'''Chelsea'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Premier League]]: [[2005\u201306 FA Premier League|2005\u201306]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/players/2457/Hern\u00e1n-Crespo/overview |title=Hern\u00e1n Crespo: Overview |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=16 April 2018}}</ref>\n*[[FA Community Shield]]: [[2005 FA Community Shield|2005]]\n\n'''Inter Milan'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[2006\u201307 Serie A|2006\u201307]], [[2007\u201308 Serie A|2007\u201308]], [[2008\u201309 Serie A|2008\u201309]]\n*Supercoppa Italiana: [[2006 Supercoppa Italiana|2006]], [[2008 Supercoppa Italiana|2008]]\n\n'''Argentina'''<ref name=SW/>\n*[[Pan American Games]]: [[Football at the 1995 Pan American Games|1995]]\n*[[Summer Olympic Games|Summer Olympics]] runner-up: [[Football at the 1996 Summer Olympics|1996]]\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[List of Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n top scorers|Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n top scorer]]: [[1993\u201394 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|1993\u201394]]\n*[[Football at the Summer Olympics]] [[Football at the 1996 Summer Olympics \